    • Method Detail

      • check

        public void check​(Path file,
                  PageCursor cursor,
                  Root root,
                  GBPTreeConsistencyCheckVisitor<KEY> visitor,
                  PageCursorTracer cursorTracer)
           throws IOException
        Checks so that all pages between IdSpace.MIN_TREE_NODE_ID and highest allocated id are either in use in the tree, on the free-list or free-list nodes.
        Parameters:
        file - The file containing the gbptree
        cursor - PageCursor to use for reading.
        root - Root the root of the gbptree.
        visitor - GBPTreeConsistencyCheckVisitor visitor to report inconsistencies to.
        cursorTracer - underlying page cursor tracer
        Throws:
        IOException - on PageCursor error.
